  <div class="icons"><span class="icon icon-landmark">Landmark</span></div>
  <p class="entry-meta"><span class="entry-tag">West Chelsea / High Line</span><span class="entry-tag">Residential</span></p>
  <p class="entry-blurb">11-story residential building directly adjacent to the High Line. Fluid stainless steel facade with sculpted balconies — Hadid's only completed residential building in New York, and one of her last projects before her death in 2016. The section engages the High Line at multiple levels.</p>
  <a class="map-link" href="https://maps.google.com/?q=520+W+28th+St,+New+York,+NY+10001" target="_blank">↗ 520 W 28th St</a>
