  <p class="entry-blurb">Danny Meyer's Union Square Hospitality Group, 2004. Started as a hot dog cart to benefit the Madison Square Park Conservancy. The original permanent kiosk in the park is the location — the ShackBurger, crinkle fries, and concrete custard shakes at the source. There are now 500 locations worldwide; this is the one that matters.</p>
  <a class="map-link" href="https://maps.google.com/?q=Madison+Square+Park,+New+York,+NY+10010" target="_blank">↗ Madison Square Park</a>
</div>

<!-- ── MARKETS + EVENTS ── -->
<div class="borough-header">Markets + Events</div>

<div class="entry" data-type="market event" data-cuisine="" data-cost="$" data-hood="midtown">
