  <div class="entry-row"><span class="entry-label">Flea Market</span><span class="entry-cost">Free entry</span></div>
  <h2 class="entry-title">Brooklyn Flea</h2>
  <div class="icons"><span class="icon icon-iconic">⊙ Iconic</span><span class="icon icon-free">Free</span></div>
  <p class="entry-meta"><span class="entry-tag">Dumbo — Saturdays year-round</span><span class="entry-tag">Chelsea Flea — Sundays year-round</span></p>
  <p class="entry-blurb">Jonathan Butler and Eric Demby, 2008. Vintage furniture, clothing, records, jewelry, art. The Dumbo Saturday market under the Manhattan Bridge overpass is the flagship. Brooklyn Flea also runs Chelsea Flea on Sundays in Manhattan year-round. One of the best flea markets in the country.</p>
  <a class="map-link" href="https://maps.google.com/?q=Brooklyn+Flea,+Dumbo,+Brooklyn,+NY" target="_blank">↗ Dumbo, Brooklyn (Sat)</a>
</div>

<!-- ── NIGHTLIFE ── -->
<div class="borough-header">Nightlife</div>

<div class="entry" data-type="nightlife" data-cuisine="" data-cost="$$" data-hood="red-hook">
