  <h2 class="entry-title">Public Records</h2>
  <p class="entry-meta"><span class="entry-tag">Gowanus, Brooklyn</span><span class="entry-tag">Thu–Sat til 4am</span></p>
  <p class="entry-blurb">Former ASPCA headquarters on the Gowanus Canal. Francis Harris (Music from Memory label) runs programming. Five spaces: Sound Room with a custom OJAS/Ojeda quadraphonic system, Atrium bar, vegan café, UPSTAIRS lounge, and outdoor plant nursery. Electronic music, experimental jazz, ambient. Esquire best bar in America, 2020. No-frills door, no dress code.</p>
  <a class="map-link" href="https://maps.google.com/?q=233+Butler+St,+Brooklyn,+NY+11217" target="_blank">↗ 233 Butler St</a>
</div>

<div class="entry" data-type="nightlife" data-cuisine="" data-cost="$" data-hood="bushwick-greenpoint">
