  <div class="entry-row"><span class="entry-label">Club</span><span class="entry-cost">$</span></div>
  <h2 class="entry-title">Good Room</h2>
  <p class="entry-meta"><span class="entry-tag">Greenpoint, Brooklyn</span><span class="entry-tag">Fri–Sat til late</span></p>
  <p class="entry-blurb">Opened 2014. Underground house and techno, disco. d&amp;b audiotechnik sound system, fog machine, central disco ball, ~200 capacity. Inclusive door — the most consistent small club in Brooklyn. "Specializing in late nights and disco lights."</p>
  <a class="map-link" href="https://maps.google.com/?q=98+Meserole+Ave,+Brooklyn,+NY+11222" target="_blank">↗ 98 Meserole Ave</a>
</div>

