  <h2 class="entry-title">Elsewhere</h2>
  <p class="entry-meta"><span class="entry-tag">Bushwick, Brooklyn</span><span class="entry-tag">Thu–Sat til late</span></p>
  <p class="entry-blurb">Three floors: Great Hall (main room, 700 cap), Zone 1 (intimate, 200 cap), Loft, rooftop (summer). Underground and unbound — live bands, techno DJs, hip-hop, queer nights including Papi Juice. Tickets in advance via website. The best multi-room booking in Brooklyn for serious lineups.</p>
  <a class="map-link" href="https://maps.google.com/?q=599+Johnson+Ave,+Brooklyn,+NY+11237" target="_blank">↗ 599 Johnson Ave</a>
</div>

