  <h2 class="entry-title">Nowadays</h2>
  <p class="entry-meta"><span class="entry-tag">Ridgewood, Queens</span><span class="entry-tag">Mister Sunday (outdoor, summer) + Nonstop (24hr weekends)</span></p>
  <p class="entry-blurb">Eamon Harkin and Justin Carter of Mister Saturday Night / Mister Sunday. 16,000 sq ft: outdoor padded dance floor under honey locust trees (summer), Indoors warehouse club with custom sound and marble bar. Free water and earplugs always. Gender-neutral bathrooms. Sliding scale door. Nonstop 24-hour parties every weekend since 2024 — the first licensed venue in NYC to do so. The most considered nightlife project in the city.</p>
  <a class="map-link" href="https://maps.google.com/?q=56-06+Cooper+Ave,+Ridgewood,+NY+11385" target="_blank">↗ 56-06 Cooper Ave</a>
</div>

