  <p class="entry-meta"><span class="entry-tag">East Williamsburg, Brooklyn</span><span class="entry-tag">Seasonal (Mirage: May–Oct)</span></p>
  <p class="entry-blurb">The largest club complex in NYC. Brooklyn Mirage outdoor stage completely renovated 2025 — new monumental timber canopy structure, 197ft × 164ft, 65ft above the crowd. Boiler Room, major techno and house bookings, multi-day festivals. King's Hall indoor room for smaller shows year-round. When you want scale.</p>
