  <div class="entry-row"><span class="entry-label">Books — New</span><span class="entry-cost">$</span></div>
  <h2 class="entry-title">McNally Jackson</h2>
  <p class="entry-meta"><span class="entry-tag">Nolita (flagship) + Williamsburg, Seaport, Downtown Brooklyn, Rockefeller Center</span><span class="entry-tag">Since 2004</span></p>
  <p class="entry-blurb">Sarah McNally's independent. Five locations. Strong backlist, international literature, small press, art magazines. Frontlist buying done by McNally herself. The serious independent option in a city that has lost most of its serious independents.</p>
  <a class="map-link" href="https://maps.google.com/?q=McNally+Jackson+Books,+134+Mulberry+St,+New+York,+NY+10013" target="_blank">↗ 134 Mulberry St, Nolita</a>
