  <p class="entry-meta"><span class="entry-tag">SoHo — Crosby St</span><span class="entry-tag">Nonprofit</span></p>
  <p class="entry-blurb">Non-profit used bookstore. All proceeds fund Housing Works' HIV/homelessness services. Donated stock from estates and private collections — design, art, and photography sections are exceptional. The Crosby Street space has a café and hosts regular literary events. The best hunting ground for serious books in Manhattan.</p>
  <a class="map-link" href="https://maps.google.com/?q=126+Crosby+St,+New+York,+NY+10012" target="_blank">↗ 126 Crosby St</a>
