  <h2 class="entry-title">Printed Matter</h2>
  <p class="entry-meta"><span class="entry-tag">Chelsea — 231 11th Ave</span><span class="entry-tag">Founded 1976 by Sol LeWitt + Lucy Lippard</span></p>
  <p class="entry-blurb">Non-profit dedicated to artists' publications. 15,000 titles by 6,000 artists. Zines, limited editions, artist-made books, small press ephemera — publications that exist outside mainstream distribution. Founded by a consortium including Sol LeWitt and Lucy Lippard. The only institution of its kind in North America.</p>
  <a class="map-link" href="https://maps.google.com/?q=231+11th+Ave,+New+York,+NY+10001" target="_blank">↗ 231 11th Ave, Chelsea</a>
