  <p class="entry-blurb">The best selection of used classical LPs and CDs in the city, plus strong jazz, rock, and avant-garde. $1 bins. The East 12th Street store is the original LP-focused location; the 18th Street store specializes in CDs. In-house label reissues uncommon African psychedelic recordings.</p>
