  <p class="entry-blurb">Japanese "no-brand" philosophy — neutral colors, no logos, functional design. Stationery, storage, travel goods, bedding, housewares, skincare. The SoHo flagship is the largest in North America. Affordable and consistent.</p>
  <a class="map-link" href="https://maps.google.com/?q=455+Broadway,+New+York,+NY+10013" target="_blank">↗ 455 Broadway, SoHo</a>
