  <p class="entry-meta"><span class="entry-tag">Midtown (museum) + SoHo — 81 Spring St</span></p>
  <p class="entry-blurb">Objects meeting eight strict design criteria. Eames, Noguchi, and Cattelan exclusives alongside accessible contemporary pieces. The SoHo location at 81 Spring is the more browsable of the two — less tourist pressure than the museum shop. Architecture and design book selection is strong.</p>
