  <p class="entry-meta"><span class="entry-tag">MIT Campus</span><span class="entry-tag">Civic + Academic</span></p>
  <p class="entry-blurb">414,000 sq ft housing MIT's computer science, AI, and linguistics departments. A collision of tilted, angled, and cylindrical volumes in aluminum, brick, and painted steel. Significant post-occupancy failures in drainage and maintenance, and substantial litigation.</p>
  <a class="map-link" href="https://maps.google.com/?q=32+Vassar+St,+Cambridge,+MA+02139" target="_blank">↗ 32 Vassar St</a>
