  <div class="entry-row"><span class="entry-label">Sert, Josep Lluís</span><span class="entry-cost">1964</span></div>
  <h2 class="entry-title">BU Law Tower Campus</h2>
  <p class="entry-meta"><span class="entry-tag">Boston University</span><span class="entry-tag">Civic + Academic</span></p>
  <p class="entry-blurb">Sert's largest assembled complex — five buildings along Commonwealth Avenue reorienting BU toward the Charles River. The 18-story Law Tower anchors a podium of connected low-rise buildings. Board-formed concrete. Docomomo-listed as the most innovative high-rise of its period in New England.</p>
  <a class="map-link" href="https://maps.google.com/?q=765+Commonwealth+Ave,+Boston,+MA+02215" target="_blank">↗ 765 Commonwealth Ave</a>
</div>

<div class="entry" data-type="residential" data-hood="harvard" data-arch="sert">
