  <p class="entry-blurb">A 7-mile continuous chain of nine parks and parkways — one of the earliest examples of urban green infrastructure in the world. Connects the Back Bay Fens through Jamaica Pond, Arnold Arboretum, and Franklin Park. Walkable or bikeable end-to-end.</p>
